    "body": "## Problem\r\nDiagnostic highlight groups were applied by iterating and calling `vim.hl.range` for each group individually. That resulted in multiple extmarks with the same priority being created separately, which does not allow `DiagnosticUnnecessary` and `DiagnosticDeprecated` with matching options override `Diagnostic*` styling.\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\nPass the list of hl-groups to `vim.hl.range` so they are applied together in the correct order.\r\n\r\nFix #38649",
    "closed_at": null,
